text: Ate iha sabhava nahim si ki imana vale sare nikala kharhe hona. Tam ajiha ki'um na ho'i'a ki unham de hareka dala vicom ika varaga nikala ke a'unda, uha dharama vica gahiri samajha paida karada ate vapisa ja ke apani kauma de lokam nu savadhana karada tam ki uha vi alaha tom darana vale banade
